---
import Layout from '@/layouts/main-layout.astro'
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import Card from '@/components/card.astro'
---

<Layout>
  <main class="flex size-full flex-col gap-9">
    <div class="flex gap-3">
      <h1 class="font-family-heading text-5xl font-black sm:text-6xl">
        Experience
      </h1>
      <Image
        src="https://fonts.gstatic.com/s/e/notoemoji/latest/2728/512.gif"
        aria-hidden="true"
        alt=""
        width="96"
        height="96"
        class="size-[48px] sm:size-[60px]"
      />
    </div>
    <!-- Timeline Container -->
    <div class="relative mx-auto w-full">
      <!-- Vertical Line (Mobile: left, Desktop: center) -->
      <div
        class="absolute top-0 bottom-0 left-0 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-black md:left-1/2 md:-translate-x-1/2"
      >
      </div>

      <!-- Timeline Items -->
      <div class="space-y-9">
        <!-- Item 1 -->
        <div class="relative md:flex md:items-center">
          <!-- Dot -->
          <div
            class="absolute top-0 left-[-9px] z-10 size-6 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-primary md:left-1/2 md:-translate-x-1/2"
          >
          </div>
          <!-- Content Card (Mobile: right, Desktop: alternates) -->
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-8">
            <Card class="ml-8 md:ml-0">
              <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Reynaers Aluminium</h3>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Feb 2025 - Present</p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
                <p>
                  At Reynaers Aluminium, I contributed as a front-end developer
                  to the creation of a <b>secure, user-friendly AI chatbot</b>.
                </p>
                <p>
                  I improved the UI using modern technologies, refactored the
                  codebase, and helped deliver an
                  <b> intuitive solution</b>.
                </p>
              </div>
            </Card>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Item 2 -->
        <div class="relative md:flex md:flex-row-reverse md:items-center">
          <!-- Dot -->
          <div
            class="absolute top-0 left-[-9px] z-10 size-6 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-primary md:left-1/2 md:-translate-x-1/2"
          >
          </div>
          <!-- Content Card (Mobile: right, Desktop: alternates) -->
          <div class="mt-6 md:mt-0 md:w-1/2 md:pl-8">
            <Card class="ml-8 md:ml-0">
              <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Katoen Natie</h3>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Dec 2019 - Jan 2025</p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
                <p>
                  At Katoen Natie, I worked in various teams where I combined
                  front-end development with <b>team guidance</b> and close collaboration
                  with others.
                </p>
                <p>
                  I contributed to invoicing, warehouse management, and site
                  visit applications. I also played a <b>key role</b> in the development
                  of the Hexagon <b>design system</b>.
                </p>
              </div>
            </Card>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Item 3 -->
        <div class="relative md:flex md:items-center">
          <!-- Dot -->
          <div
            class="absolute top-0 left-[-9px] z-10 size-6 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-primary md:left-1/2 md:-translate-x-1/2"
          >
          </div>
          <!-- Content Card (Mobile: right, Desktop: alternates) -->
          <div class="mt-6 md:mt-0 md:w-1/2 md:pr-8">
            <Card class="ml-8 md:ml-0">
              <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Pelckmans Uitgevers</h3>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Jul 2018 - Oct 2019</p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
                <p>
                  During my time at Pelckmans Publishers, I contributed to
                  digital
                  <b>learning platforms</b>, most notably a virtual whiteboard.
                </p>
                <p>
                  These projects taught me how technology can make education
                  more
                  <b>accessible</b> and <b>effective</b> for both students and teachers.
                </p>
              </div>
            </Card>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Item 4 -->
        <div class="relative md:flex md:flex-row-reverse md:items-center">
          <!-- Dot -->
          <div
            class="absolute top-0 left-[-9px] z-10 size-6 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-primary md:left-1/2 md:-translate-x-1/2"
          >
          </div>
          <!-- Content Card (Mobile: right, Desktop: alternates) -->
          <div class="mt-6 md:mt-0 md:w-1/2 md:pl-8">
            <Card class="ml-8 md:ml-0">
              <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Euricom Studio</h3>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Sep 2017 - May 2018</p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
                <p>
                  In between projects I contributed to applications where I
                  combined technical and analytical skills to develop
                  <b> user-friendly and efficient </b>solutions.
                </p>
                <p>
                  For instance, I worked on a web application for video
                  interviews and modernized Euricom's website using a
                  <b> static site generator </b>
                  and CMS integration.
                </p>
              </div>
            </Card>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Item 5 -->
        <div class="relative md:flex md:items-center">
          <!-- Dot -->
          <div
            class="absolute top-0 left-[-9px] z-10 size-6 rounded-full border-2 border-black bg-primary md:left-1/2 md:-translate-x-1/2"
          >
          </div>
          <!-- Content Card (Mobile: right, Desktop: alternates) -->
          <div class="mt-6 md:mt-0 md:w-1/2 md:pr-8">
            <Card class="ml-8 md:ml-0">
              <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Jstack</h3>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Nov 2017 - Apr 2018</p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
                <p>
                  While working at Jstack, I was involved in the development of
                  Carcollect, a digital tool aimed at streamlining
                  <b> taxation and car transactions</b>.
                </p>
                <p>
                  As a junior developer, I quickly learned to work with
                  <b> React </b>
                  and actively contributed to improving both the frontend and backend
                  of the application.
                </p>
              </div>
            </Card>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
